            <title>Nepal</title>
            <h1>Beautiful Places  Nepal</h1>
            <p>Nepal is one of the most visited and explored country among all other countries of the world. Although, it is a landlocked country, surrounded by china and india , it is one of the most beautiful country geographically.
                It is divided into: Himalayan region, Hilly region and Terai region; where himalayan region covers about 15% of total land area , Hilly region covers about 68% and terai about 17%.</p>
                <h2>Places to visit in Nepal</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Solukhumbu (for tallest mountain of world:Mount Everest)</li>
                    <li>Bhaktapur (for its ancient history and temples)</li>
                    <li>Pokhara (for lakes and beauty of natural geography)</li>
                    <li>Jumla and Humla (for apple farms)</li>
                    
                </ol>
                <p>Among 10 tallest mountains of the world, top 8 mountains lies in Nepal and Mount Everest also lies in Nepal height of about 8849m(December 2025) currently.</p>
                
